GREATER CHINA DAYBOOK: Hong Kong Land Auction; PetroChina, Agbank Earnings

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-04-26T22:14:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/greater-china-daybook-hong-kong-land-auction-agribank-petrochina-nets.html
Hong Kong ’s government will sell a
residential building site today in its first land auction since
imposing the toughest measures yet to curb  home prices  in
November.  The site on Ko Shan Road in the Hung Hom district, close to
the site of the city’s former airport, may fetch HK$1.3 billion
($167 million), according to the median estimate of five
surveyors and analysts surveyed by Bloomberg News. The estimates
range from HK$1.07 billion to HK$1.53 billion.  The auction starts at 2:30 p.m. local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net . 